OL,3,CHospital admits to 'failings' in care
OL,4,Cof autistic boy who died of sepsis
OL,6,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,7,FNews, the day before the inquest into
OL,8,Fhis death, Mattheus Vieira's
OL,9,Fheartbroken parents described him as
OL,10,F"special", adding: "And special in a
OL,11,Fgood way, not just special needs."
OL,13,F"People may think because he was
OL,14,Fautistic he was difficult, but it's
OL,15,Fnot the case, he was very easy.
OL,17,F"He was the boss of the house, we just
OL,18,Fmiss his presence."
