OL,3,CHospital admits to 'failings' in care
OL,4,Cof autistic boy who died of sepsis
OL,6,FMattheus, aged 11, was taken to King's
OL,7,FLynn Hospital, in Norfolk, with a
OL,8,Fkidney infection. He struggled to cope
OL,9,Fwith medical staff taking
OL,10,Fobservations, and his notes recorded
OL,11,Fhim as "uncooperative".
OL,13,FHis dad, Vitor Vieira, told ITV News:
OL,14,F"He doesn't like to be touched, even a
OL,15,Fplaster he doesn't like.
OL,17,F"And they say 'Oh he does not co-
OL,18,Foperate'. He was an autistic boy, what
OL,19,Fdo you expect?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
