OL,3,CHospital admits to 'failings' in care
OL,4,Cof autistic boy who died of sepsis
OL,6,FMr Vieira said: "We're not here for
OL,7,Frevenge. We don't hate anyone.
OL,9,F"We just don't want it to happen
OL,10,Fagain. We know a lot of autistic boys
OL,11,Fand girls from school. They are lovely
OL,12,Fchildren, they deserve better."
OL,14,FIt is now mandatory for all
OL,15,Fappropriate NHS staff to receive
OL,16,Ftraining on learning disabilities and
OL,17,Fautism.
OL,19,FITV News asked all NHS hospital trusts
OL,20,Fin England if the relevant staff had
OL,21,Fcompleted the training.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
