OL,6,FOut of those who responded, 64 (86%)
OL,7,Fof trusts said they had not.
OL,9,FReacting to those figures, Mr Vieira
OL,10,Fsaid: "I'm not saying they don't care,
OL,11,Fthey do care, but I think the training
OL,12,Fis not there and they need to do
OL,13,Fbetter.
OL,15,F"They need to understand people with
OL,16,Fdisabilities, physical and mental
OL,17,Fwhatever. They need to do better, they
OL,18,Fneed to learn."
